Subject: [PATCH 1841/1851] media: v4l2-core: introduce a helper to unregister
 a i2c subdev

commit 1a065ee3e97cc58ab900ccb7eb2b421fdab1d0dc upstream

Introduce a new video4linux2 i2c helper, to unregister a subdev.
This allows to get rid of yet another ifdef.

